e ring current\nregion is comparable to or even greater than that of EMIC wave scattering. Our\nresults suggest the non-negligible effects of the FLCS and should be considered\nin radiation belt and ring current modeling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Mar 2023 15:16:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-14"}
